      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good in theory, but \"the vast majority\" is a bit vague for me. I've seen other NGOs where admin and marketing end up taking 30% or 40% of the total. Can you give me a concrete percentage? What exact portion of this $1M is going directly to field operations in South Sudan?",
